data.description: Wow! Brick rancher on half an acre. Convenient location. Sitting on a large double lot, this home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with double garage with plenty of room to move around and a fenced back yard. Updated hardwoods, bathrooms & kitchen backsplash. Lots of room in closets and two different attic spaces over garage that offer lots of storage along with partial basement that is accessed from outside. Lots of extras with a reasonable offer.
